title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Adapting to an unexpected upset to your plans becomes satisfying if you can sidestep your initial annoyance. Youre not necessarily irritated by altering your schedule since youre probably flexible, anyway. But its harder to tweak your expectations than rearrange todays timetable. Stay open by releasing yourself from any preconceptions that you know how the day will unfold. Control is a delusion now, while wonder and enchantment are as real as granite rock. Miracles happen if youre willing to stick around more for the magic than to manipulate reality to your liking. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
